Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:20.44,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:23.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:29.46,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:41.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:54.63,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:57.64,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:08.33,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:14.30,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:20.13,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.54,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.69,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.86,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:34.93,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:36.15,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:43.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:50.26,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:56.99,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:01.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:09.00,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:17.69,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:25.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…恶魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸 别怯阵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是堂堂的坎贝尔家家主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立交易都市 三号街自卫骑士团所属
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经 是第三次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:46.14,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur3}骑士 -Knight-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs42}{\blur2}独立交易都市 豪斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 今天的蔬菜打七折哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上刚网的鱼 条条活蹦乱跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不瞒您说 玉钢的交易价格从年初就定了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你再便宜点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定？ 要知道帝国的重臣也敬我三分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逼我把话说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这里是独立交易都市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国也好 军国也罢 都管不着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想买的话 就请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你这乡巴佬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人 只要帝国有心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…自卫骑士团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉钢买卖方面 豪斯曼拥有独占权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国应该最清楚不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知还要强买的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先问过我这把坎贝尔家族之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好 塞西莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 迷上你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是女大十八变啊 当初的塞西莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别色迷迷地看人家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 那件铠甲虽然破旧 却也是上品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 那家伙莫非是哪里的骑士团长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 骑士的剑不是用来做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士的剑是为了保护市民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是独立交易都市 三号街自卫骑士团所属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一遍 放下武器投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续胡作非为的话 我来做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我…得不到救赎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这就是…实战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了战斗不惜舍弃身心与灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么却…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畏惧  不要退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用来保护市民的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坎贝尔家族…之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这支胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次战争的幸存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剑…削断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那样的剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢相助 我是三号街…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起的骑士阁下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 等等我啊 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女骑士很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 那种笨拙的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么霸气十足？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更难收场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没注意看脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说到底算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥舞着那种古董品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有仔细看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那个人的剑折断了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好机会 早点对骑士死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不是那边哦 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没心情了 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 今天有重要的会议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 卢克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近多是这样使用铸模锻造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断剑只能融化后重新打造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 这把剑就不再是这把剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是坎贝尔家世代相传的宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前倒是有过能够修剑的铁匠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在找起来谈何容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也为骑士团锻造佩剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以提供相同造型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我明白 但还是喜欢这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情虽然能够理解 但这把剑也到寿命了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算勉强修复 估计也不能用于实战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言它有特殊意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无可替代的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识一个叫卢克的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 卢克？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号街偏远处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河畔旁 灰森林入口附近的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里就快完了 喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是独立交易都市 三号街自卫骑士团所属
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前日承蒙你出手相救 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆滑的人际关系 要从寒暄开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲教给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招呼打完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用 坎贝尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我塞西莉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫利萨吧 和店名一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店名是丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 你有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你为我铸剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想拥有那样的宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能斩断其他剑的宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们店不接受铸剑委托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑的锻造从老爸那代就废止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是老爸锻的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那刚才你用的剑也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是卢克锻造的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没什么好隐瞒的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的剑比我迄今为止见过的任何剑都锋利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为我铸一把那样的剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝 我只为我自己铸刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀？ 你是指那把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的剑 坎贝尔家家主代代相传的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不可一世的自称骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实一个月前刚刚受封
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坎贝尔家从恶魔契约战争时期开始 就作为骑士参战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为初代豪斯曼的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造起了这座独立交易都市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并支撑它守护至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从祖父到父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而父亲在一月前病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为独生女 决心继承父亲的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坎贝尔家的当家人 世世代代都必须是骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在前日的初次实战中 险些丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手持祖父和父亲传承下来的这把剑战斗到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我唯一的心灵寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要一把不会折断的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我的半身 支撑我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捍卫骑士的荣耀 捍卫这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要一把能够能成为我伙伴的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我铸吧 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会折断的 只属于我的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上不存在不会断的剑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论造得多么结实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会寿终正寝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是卢克锻造的刀也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说的不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 请认真看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大胆呢 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么冷酷无情的男人我才不放在眼里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够狠的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是突然的告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要畏惧 保护货物！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 这里会有「人外」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}人外：和人拥有同样内脏机能的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团遇到「人外」也威风不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝马上就会到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被山贼…袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物就拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗 骑士的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「人外」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子被人操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你在这里看着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为骑士是否有资格使用你铸造的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个傻丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口气比力气大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 人外不是王牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来只能赶快开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是什么王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留有一手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心脏知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接二连三地让你救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 丧心病狂的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔契约！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔契约？ 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆 还不快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别但是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一无所能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你疯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 "请认真看着我"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是独立交易都市 三号街自卫骑士团所属
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂的坎贝尔家家主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的职责是保护这座城市 也是保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我吧 卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我 塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨 玉钢和刀柄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 为我争取少许时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锻造开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:21:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水挫 小割 选别 积重 锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折返 折返 折返
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折返 折返
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯铁成形 皮铁成形 造边 素延 造锋 火造 粗研 覆土 淬火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧入 锻造研 初研
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备水砥 改正砥 中名仓砥 细名仓砥 内昙地砥 修饰研磨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀艳地砥 拭刀 取刀 打磨 刀帽研磨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收柄！
